<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Approval Request</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 style="color: #333;">Approval Request for {{projectName}}</h1>
    <p>You have been requested to review and approve the following item:</p>
    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;">
      <p>{{approvalDetails}}</p>
    </div>
    <p>Please review this item in the JasaWeb Client Portal and provide your approval or feedback.</p>
    <a href="{{approvalLink}}" style="background-color: #007cba; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 10px 0;">
      Review & Approve
    </a>
    <br>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact your project manager.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The JasaWeb Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>